<div class="cover anystretch info-intro" data-stretch="images/goaprop2.jpg">
	<div class="content-block">
		<div class="inner">
			<h3>Sell OR Lease your property</h3>
			<p>Kindly give us a "brief description" of the type of property you would like us to represent, and we will get in touch with you.</p>
		</div>
